Package fr.ferret.model

Class Zone

java.lang.Object
fr.ferret.model.Zone
Direct Known Subclasses:
Region
public class Zone extends Object
A world zone of the 1KG project.
It contains a set of people, a name and an abbrev, and may be part of a Region.

For example the Europe Region (EUR) should contain the following The zones : CEU, GBR, FIN, IBS and TSI.
This can vary according to the selected Phase1KG phase.

    • of

      public static Set<Zone> of(Map<String,Set<String>> zones)
      Creates a Set of zones from a sample map. The keys of this map are the abbreviations of the zones, and the values are sets of String corresponding to the people contained in each zone (each String is the id of a people, like HG00121)
      Parameters:
      zones - The sample Map to create the zones from
      Returns:
      The Set of zones.
